A. Introduction:
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
The purpose of this document is to assist new wizards in beginning their
coding efforts in Ansalon domain. Consider this a guideline of what should
be followed when you code, and what you might want to use to help with your
coding. There are a few rules as to the format to be used when writing code.
In addition, there are wizard tools available to help you stay informed,
and to assist you in your coding and debugging efforts.
The last sections of this document pertain to wizard behavior, particulary
on the mortal realm, and when playing mortal second characters. Please read
that portion carefully.

